# Zuba

Zuba is an online shop selling Rwandan cultural materials, including decorations, jewelry, clothing, paintings, and more. We directly export our products from Rwanda to Canada, ensuring freshness and authenticity for our customers.

## Description

Zuba aims to bridge the gap between Rwandan culture and Canadian consumers by offering a diverse range of cultural items. Our shop not only showcases beautiful crafts but also tells the story of Rwandan heritage. The project features:

- User-Friendly Interface: Easy navigation and a seamless shopping experience.
- Cultural Diversity: A variety of products that highlight Rwandan craftsmanship.
- irect Sourcing: Products are directly exported from Rwanda, ensuring quality and freshness.

### Technologies Used

- Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript (with  React)
- Backend: Node.js, Express 
- Database: MongoDB, MySQL 
- Version Control: Git, GitHub

## Getting Started

